data.description: Seller to contribute $2,500.00 toward closing cost for qualified buyer.  150 Salesbarn Road. A completely renovated 3 bedroom/1 bathroom home, updated with modern appointments throughout, including a garage with an automatic garage door! The interior of this home was taken to the studs so the flooring, carpet, doors and hardware, sheetrock, trim, plumbing, electrical wiring, insulation, and dual pane windows are all new! Also new is the roof, roof decking, all appliances, as well as its major systems the HVAC system and hot water heater. The home features an open concept kitchen, family and dining space that opens onto a new backyard deck. The kitchen features new white cabinetry, SS appliances, gas range, quartz counter tops and coordinating backsplash. The new bathroom makes the most efficient use of the space, as does the new and large laundry room, with washer and dryer included. To enhance its curb appeal, the brick exterior was painted and a front stoop entrance added. Located on over a half acre, the home is ideally located off Bankhead Highway and offers ease of access to I-20, to the University of West Georgia, and is just minutes to downtown Carrollton with shopping and restaurants!  Lender credit toward closing cost for eligible purchasers that will be owner occupants and approved by listing agent's preferred lender.
